reviewText: John Branyan is one of my favorite comedians.  He makes everyday events hilarious without being raunchy.  Good, clean, fun the whole family can enjoy.

John Branyan is hiliarious !!! We have watched this one a few times and still enjoy it so much. We have showed it to a few friends , including children and they have all enjoyed it as much as we have. It is so nice to have good clean jokes to get so much enjoyment and laughs out of . I will be looking for more of his dvd's !
